title: PIP03 - Development roadmap
body:
In line with the discussion on the governance forum https://gov.pangolin.exchange/t/pip03-development-roadmap/744 we'll open the voting on what the priority should be on the development roadmap.

The item with the highest votes will be worked on in order of priority.
author: 0x72C397908Cb93d1B569BBB0Ff8d3D26B7b21d730
